\/2017\/06\/12\/pregnancy-women-break-fasting\/","url_meta":{"origin":35675,"position":0},"title":"Ibn Abbas on Ramadan: Pregnant women have permission to break fast","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"June 12, 2017","format":false,"excerpt":"Sa\u2019id ibn Jubayr reported: Ibn Abbas, may Allah be pleased with him, said, \u201cIf a pregnant woman fears for herself and the nursing of her child during Ramadan, she should break her fast and in place of each day feed a poor person. She does not need to make up\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Quran Exegesis \u0627\u0644\u062a\u0641\u0633\u064a\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Quran Exegesis \u0627\u0644\u062a\u0641\u0633\u064a\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/quran-exegesis-tafsir\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":38824,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2023\/02\/18\/punishment-urine\/","url_meta":{"origin":35675,"position":1},"title":"Hadith on Cleanliness: Punishment in grave due to soiling yourself","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"February 18, 2023","format":false,"excerpt":"Ibn Abbas reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cThe majority of torment in the grave is due to carelessness with urine, so avoid soiling yourself with urine.\u201d Source: Sunan al-Da\u0304raqut\u0323ni\u0304 466 Grade: Sahih (authentic) according to Al-Albani \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0650 \u0627\u0628\u0652\u0646\u0650 \u0639\u064e\u0628\u064e\u0651\u0627\u0633\u064d \u0623\u064e\u0646\u064e\u0651 \u0631\u064e\u0633\u064f\u0648\u0644\u064e \u0627\u0644\u0644\u0647\u0650 \u0635\u064e\u0644\u064e\u0651\u0649\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/sin-al-ithm\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":15610,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2013\/08\/07\/ramadan-umrah-hajj\/","url_meta":{"origin":35675,"position":2},"title":"Hadith on Pilgrimage: &#8216;Umrah in Ramadan equal to Hajj","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"August 7, 2013","format":false,"excerpt":"Ibn Abbas reported: The Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \"Verily, the 'Umrah pilgrimage during Ramadan is equal to Hajj.\" Source: S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 al-Bukha\u0304ri\u0304 1782, S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 Muslim 1256 Grade: Muttafaqun Alayhi\u00a0(authenticity agreed upon) according to Al-Bukhari and Muslim \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0627\u0628\u0652\u0646\u0650 \u0639\u064e\u0628\u0651\u064e\u0627\u0633\u064d \u0623\u064e\u0646\u0651\u064e \u0627\u0644\u0646\u0651\u064e\u0628\u0650\u064a\u0651\u064e \u0635\u064e\u0644\u0651\u064e\u0649 \u0627\u0644\u0644\u0651\u064e\u0647\u064f \u0639\u064e\u0644\u064e\u064a\u0652\u0647\u0650 \u0648\u064e\u0633\u064e\u0644\u0651\u064e\u0645\u064e \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e \u0625\u0650\u0646\u0651\u064e\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/righteousness-al-birr\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":27620,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2019\/04\/16\/break-fast-intending-travel\/","url_meta":{"origin":35675,"position":3},"title":"Hadith on Travel: Permission to break fast before intending to travel","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"April 16, 2019","format":false,"excerpt":"Muhammad ibn Ka\u2019b reported: I came to Anas ibn Malik, may Allah be pleased with him, during Ramadan and he intended to travel. His mount was prepared for him and he put on his traveling clothes. He called for some food and he ate it. I said to him, \u201cIs\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":36130,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2021\/05\/11\/laylat-al-qadr-last-night\/","url_meta":{"origin":35675,"position":4},"title":"Hadith on Ramadan: Seek Laylat al-Qadr on last night of Ramadan","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"May 11, 2021","format":false,"excerpt":"Mu\u2019awiyah ibn Abi Sufyan reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cSeek the Night of Decree on the last night of Ramadan.\u201d Source: S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 Ibn Khuzaymah 2189 Grade: Sahih (authentic) according to Al-Albani \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0645\u064f\u0639\u064e\u0627\u0648\u0650\u064a\u064e\u0629\u064e \u0628\u0652\u0646\u0650 \u0623\u064e\u0628\u0650\u064a \u0633\u064f\u0641\u0652\u064a\u064e\u0627\u0646 \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e \u0631\u064e\u0633\u064f\u0648\u0644\u064f \u0627\u0644\u0644\u0651\u064e\u0647 \u0635\u064e\u0644\u0651\u064e\u0649 \u0627\u0644\u0644\u0651\u064e\u0647 \u0639\u064e\u0644\u064e\u064a\u0652\u0647\u0650\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":31940,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2019\/06\/10\/zakat-al-fitr-purification\/","url_meta":{"origin":35675,"position":5},"title":"Hadith on Ramadan: Zakat al-Fitr as purification for misbehavior","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"June 10, 2019","format":false,"excerpt":"Ibn Abbas reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and bles